('Are There Any Limitations On Certain Trading Practices at Funded Trader Markets?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "At Funded Trader Markets, we empower traders to choose their trading styles and strategies without restrictions. However, it is crucial to follow our guidelines and avoid activities that exploit our", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "systems or violate fair trading practices. The following actions are strictly prohibited:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Using Manipulative Software or Techniques", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Employing software, AI, ultra-high-speed techniques, or mass data entry methods that manipulate or unfairly advantage your use of our systems is not allowed.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Non-Standard Trading Practices", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Engaging in trading practices that deviate from typical forex or financial market trading, or that could cause financial or other harm to the provider.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Using External or Slow Data Feeds", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Executing trades with external or slow data feeds.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Exploiting Service Errors", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Using trading strategies that take advantage of errors in our services, such as price display errors or delayed updates.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Manipulative Trading", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Engaging in manipulative trades, such as entering simultaneous opposite positions, either individually or in collaboration with others.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Hedging Across Accounts", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Hedging between accounts with other evaluation firms similar to Funded Trader Markets", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Account Management Services", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "All accounts in our challenges must be traded exclusively by the account owner once a phase is completed. Any deviation from this rule will be considered a violation.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Additionally, only one trader per household and IP address is allowed. Breaching this rule will resu