('Adakah Terdapat Peraturan Mengenai Konsistensi untuk Akaun Standard 2-Langkah?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Untuk akaun Standard 2-langkah, terdapat peraturan konsistensi yang terpakai untuk kedua-dua Fasa Cabaran dan Fasa Dana Simulasi.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Mengapa Peraturan ini?", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Peraturan Konsistensi Pasaran Pedagang Berpendanaan mempromosikan pertumbuhan keuntungan yang stabil dan membantu pedagang mengelakkan perdagangan yang beremosi.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Butiran Penting Mengenai Peraturan Konsistensi Untuk Akaun Penilaian", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Dalam Fasa Cabaran; anda tidak seharusnya membuat lebih daripada 50% (iaitu separuh) daripada sasaran keuntungan dalam satu hari.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Dalam Fasa Simulasi Dibiayai; anda tidak seharusnya telah membuat lebih daripada 45% daripada jumlah keuntungan dalam satu hari.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Jika keuntungan dalam satu hari melebihi 50% daripada sasaran keuntungan anda dalam Fasa Cabaran atau lebih daripada 45% daripada jumlah keuntungan anda dalam Fasa Simulasi Dibiayai, anda perlu terus berdagang sehingga tiada hari yang melebihi maksimum yang dinyatakan di atas.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Bilakah Peraturan Konsistensi Diperlukan?", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Untuk akaun penilaian, ia terpakai untuk kedua-dua Fasa Cabaran dan Fasa Pembiayaan Simulasi", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Pengiraan", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "[Hari Terbaik % daripada Jumlah Keuntungan] = [Keuntungan Hari Terbaik]  [Jumlah Keuntungan] * 100", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Keuntungan Hari Terbaik bermaksud keuntungan hari tunggal tertinggi", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Keuntungan Hari Tunggal = Baki pada 5pm EST Hari Ini  Baki pada 5pm EST Semalam", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Contoh (Fasa Pembiayaan Simulasi)", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 3, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Jika anda memperoleh keuntungan keseluruhan sebanyak $5,000 dalam Fasa Pembiayaan Simulasi,", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Untuk layak mengeluarkan wang, tidak boleh ada satu hari pun dengan lebih daripada 45% daripada $5,000 (= $2,250).", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Jika terdapat satu hari dengan lebih daripada 45% daripada jumlah keuntungan, maka anda perlu terus berdagang sehingga keuntungan hari terbaik kurang daripada 45% daripada jumlah keuntungan.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Contoh (Fasa Cabaran)", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Untuk akaun $25,000 dengan sasaran keuntungan Fasa 2 sebanyak $1250 (5%), tiada keuntungan dalam satu hari seharusnya melebihi $625 (50% daripada sasaran) untuk kekal dalam peraturan konsistensi.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Jika anda mencapai keuntungan keseluruhan sebanyak $1250 tetapi memperoleh lebih daripada $625 dalam satu hari, anda dikehendaki untuk terus berdagang sehingga keuntungan hari terbaik kurang daripada 50% daripada keuntungan keseluruhan.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Kejayaan memerlukan merangka strategi yang menghalang melebihi keuntungan harian sebanyak $625.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Dengan mematuhi garis panduan ini, pedagang dapat memupuk pendekatan perdagangan yang berdisiplin dan mampan, yang penting untuk kejayaan jangka panjang.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'adakah-peraturan-mengenai-konsistensi-untuk-akaun-standard-2-langkah', 'Adakah Terdapat Peraturan Mengenai Konsistensi untuk Akaun Standard 2-Langkah?', 'Untuk akaun Standard 2-langkah, terdapat peraturan konsistensi yang terpakai untuk kedua-dua Fasa Cabaran dan Fasa Pembiayaan 