(1, 1, '68dc65fdcb943fa3c259213d', 'What is a Forex Prop Firm?', 'A Forex Prop Firm allows traders to trade with higher simulated capital while earning real money based on their consistently profitable trading skills. It enables traders to trade without risking their own funds. At Funded Trader Markets (FTM), traders can prove their skills through an Evaluation process or via simulated Instant Funded Accounts and keep a significant share of the profits they earn.', 'en'),
(2, 1, '68dc65fdcb943fa3c259213e', 'What is a Forex Funded Account?', 'A Forex Funded Account is a trading account provided by a prop firm, allowing traders to trade with large simulated capital instead of their own money. It enables skilled traders to profit without taking on huge financial risk.', 'en'),
(3, 1, '68dc65fdcb943fa3c259213f', 'How Do You Qualify for a Simulated Funded Account?', 'To qualify for a simulated funded account with FTM, you typically have two options:
